column2: From which University or Institute did you create a spinout?

column16: Did your University/TTO require a board seat in your spinout?
column17: How many months did your deal take to complete from start to finish?

column19: How much $USD did you raise in your first financing round after you spun out?
column20: How much $USD has your spinout raised in total to date?
column21: What stage is your spinout today?
